Rating: 4
I have made this salad twice as a main dish, but with two changes. I used soba noodles instead of rice and shrimp instead of crab. For some reason I never get rice right when I need to and the soba noodles are much more consistent and faster. Everyone loves this meal including my 1 and 3 year olds. I put very little dressing on the kids servings. Fun summer dish!

Rating: 4
A little time consuming, but they taste great and are a lot of fun to serve. Expect sticky rice everywhere-it lives up to its name!

